from Richardson, was riding his motorcycle the night of Aug. 24, 1998, 
and said Everett, driving an 18-wheeler, cut him off on a Dallas County 
freeway so he took out his 9 mm pistol, pulled up alongside the truck 
cab and shot him. Feldman testified at his capital murder trial that he 
was still angry about 45 minutes later when he spotted Valesquez, a 
gasoline tanker driver filling a Dallas service station, and shot him.

'A
